Parliament, Thursday, 25 October 2018 – The Portfolio Committee on Energy will tomorrow conclude its public hearings on the draft Integrated Resource Plan 2018 (IRP). Details of the public hearing are as follows: Date: Friday, 26 October 2018
	Time: 10 am
